text:
Khandu Khandelwal!!! Kaha se shuru karu bhai. Teko shayad yaad na ho, lekin apan MTH ke quiz ke baad B-bot mein mile the pehli baar. Uske baad se to aana jaana laga hi rehta tha. Apni bakchodiyo ka level hamesha se badhta hi gaya. Kitni mastiya, kitni trips aur kitni memories bana li hai bhai ab tak kehna mushkil hai.
To be honest, jab tu aaya tha collge tab kaafi kam bolta tha. Lekin dheere dheere sabke saame tera backbencher wala roop aa hi gaya. "Samosa" word sunte hi bas tere chehre ke expressions dekhne ka mann karta hai bhai aur vo dekhke mujhe bhook lagne lag jaati hai xD.
Ek aur bohot sahi quality hai tujh mein ki mehnat ke maamle mein tera koi jawaab nahi. Tere jaisi flexible biological clock mil paana bohot mushkil hai bhai. Meme world mein bhi bohot zyada progress karli hai bhai tune. Next level pe pohoch gya hai tu. Agar ek word mein tujhe describe karna ho to tujhe "khurafati dimaag" bolunga mai. Bakchodi ke liye to tu ever ready hai.
Ab peechhe mud ke dekhta hu to itne saari baatein aur memories yaad aati hai. Kaise apan ne summers mein Kaggle karne ka socha tha SoC ke saath saath. Mishra jab nahake wapas aaya tab tune kya sahi paani feka uspe aur wapas nahane pe majboor kar diya aur vo transparent cheezein jo tune Mishra se kharidwayi. Ek din mein poora Lucknow ghumna koi apan se seekhe. Kya mast time the bhai vo.
Uske baad apni Hyderabad wali trip yaad aati hai. Tujhe paneer puff pe zinda dekh ke mai aur Nitik ek doosre ko hi dekhte reh jaate the. Lekin seriously yaar dinner ki jagah koi roz paneer puff kha ke kaise apni health maintain kar sakta hai. Kabhi batana bhai kaise karta hai tu ye sab. Aur vo yaad hai roz apna oreo aur badam shake fix tha. Ramoji jaate waqt yaad hai tu kaise aage baith ke seat belt laga ke so gya tha aur bina dare vo 360 jhoole mein chala gya tha. Meri aur Nitik ki to fati thi yaar bohot (vaise Nitik ne aaj tak confess kiya nahi ye). Trekking ke time bhi tu mast neend mein hi chadhe jaa raha tha. Aur yaad hai apan ekdum raat mein Domino's aur Karachi Bakery se order karte the aur fir main gate pe jaate the order lene. Aur vo Domino's wale ke paas kaise apan plan karke gaye the jab vo late laaya tha apna order. Bohot sahi time tha yaar vo.
Goa mein bhi kya sahi maze kiye yaar apan ne. Pehle beach pe gaye jugaad dhundhne aur successful bhi rahe aur fir kaise bete ko call kiya puchhne ke liye ki jaana chahiye ki nahi. Bohot maza aaya tha bhai. Aur bohot saari trips maarni hai bhai aisi.
Loop mein Mishra ki maarke maze laa diye the bhai tune uss din. Ab to teko regularly bhand karte rahenge aur wapas uss din jaisa mahol banate rahenge. Aage bhi milta rehna bhai.

text:
Beta: Betaaa
(Long pause)
Papa: Kya hua beta?
Beta: Kya kar rahe ho?
Papa: Kuchh nahi beta.

Ye conversation as it is chali hai na jaane kitni baar. Ab to maan lo beta ki hum hi tumare papa hai. Aur kitni baar prove karna padega hume ye.

Jab pehli baar mile the apan tab hi samajh gya tha mai ki tum hi ho vo jo apne poore group ko connected rakhega. First year mein non-stop katwane se leke final year tak bakchod banna koi tumse seekhe. Tumhari yahi best quality hai ki tum nayi cheezein try karte rehte ho chahe tumhara pehle kata ho fir bhi. Ye bohot sahi quality rahi hai tumhari beta, Aur isi ke chalte tum itne bakchod bane ho. Tumhari wajah se hi hum sab saare traditions follows karte rahe hai jaise tyohar ke din mandir jaana, mithai khana, rakhi manana. Tum nahi hote to ek bohot major part nahi hota college life ka. Cheezein arrange karna, manage karna bohot ache se aata hai tumhe beta. Tumhe kuchh bhi kaho, hamesha ready rehte ho karne ke liye.

Ek aur baat hai tum mein ki tum kabhi kisi baat ka bura nahi maante. Tumhari kitni baar li hai sabne milke lekin humne kabhi tumhe udaas nahi dekha. Shayad isiliye jab tum last day roye the to humse dekha nahi gaya aur tumhe dekh ke hume bhi rona aa gya.

Goa mein kya mast maze kare the beta apan logo ne. Best trip thi vo meri aaj tak ki. Meko nahi lagta usse better trip ho payegi. Vahi roz ready hoke beach pe jaate the, khate the, nahate the aur wapas aa jaate the. Aur fir raat ko club. Aur tumhara vo dance to muahhhh, maze hi aa gaye the jab tum costume pehen ke nikle the.

Ye last mahina bhi bohot sahi mil gya apan ko college ka. Hall 1 mein protocols ki kaise aisi ki taisi ki thi apan ne aur fir last mein jab positive nikla to vo bhi D, E aur F chhod ke G mein. Maal ka arrangement to tu pehle se hi karke aaya tha. Aur usi ke kaaran quarantine sahi se kat paaya apna. Hall 12 mein to kya hi maze kiye the apan ne. Vo ek mahina best time tha meri life ka. Tumhari wajah se saare launde ek room mein jama hote the aur tumhari wajah se hi vaha baithe rehte the. Vo time hamesha yaad rahega beta.

Chalo ab agla stop aagya hai apna. Bnb book kiya ki nahi abhi tak? Nahi kiya hai to jaldi se book kardo. Bangalore mein bhi to bohot saari bakchodi karni hai aur mahol set karna hai. Aao chalo group pe Mishra ki lein firse.

text:
"Chee chee ye kya dekh liye". Yahi reaction tha mera jab maine tujhe pehli baar dekha tha xD.

Gharwalo ke jaate hi agle din bina seniors ki parwah kiye mere room pe aaya tha Pappu bhaye se milne. Yaad hai na? Ye yaad hai to fir ye bhi yaad hoga ki kaise teri class lagi thi uss din humare room mein. Blue light yaad aaya ki nahi? Uss din ke baad se to teri lene mein humne kabhi dheel nahi chhodi I guess xD.

Bina nahaye khana nahi khana, Chicken todna, tashan mein chalte chalte towel se gira diye jaana, tej banke pizza challenge haar jaana, tutorial mein so jaane pe zor se utha diye jaana, nunnu se baat baat pe jhagadna, BBQ mein leg piece laane ke liye insist karna, CCD ke bahar cycle pe kudna, Kussu se controller ke liye ladna, nunnu ko dekhne jaana lekin beech mein paani puri dekhke mud jaana, harlem shake ke time pe poori body pe powder laga dena, projects mein khali sundarta pe focus karna, khud ko Shah Rukh Khan samajh ke kaach mein apna chehra dekhna, "ganda scene" aane pe aakhein band kar lena, Messi ki t-shirt pehen ke ultra-lazy football khelna aur Linux ka man page padhte rehna jaise kai shauk rahe hai tere. Aur tera vo "Sab khana kha ke daaru pi ke chale gaye, sab chale gaye" bohot hi zyada irritating hai. Uspe to ban laga dena chahiye.

Mummy ke dikhaye raste pe chalne wala gaai aadmi kab maal maarne aur daaru peene wala paapi ban gya pata hi nahi chala. Lekin jaisa bhi hai bhai hai tu. Jab bhi mujhe low feel hota hai ya koi advice leni hoti hai to tu hi vo pehla banda rehta hai jisse mai baat karta hu. Tere bina campus life kaafi boring hoti. Aise hi padh ke nikal jaate bas.

Bas saath mein trips aur tujhe "chal-chitra" dikhana reh gaya. Mujhe aise feeling aa rahi hai ki ye dono kaam saath mein hi hone wale hai. Bete ko bol diya hai maine bnb book karane. To maa ke laadle, thoda aur bigad aur chup chap aaja Bangalore. Khoob bakchodi karenge!!

text:
Aate hi Hall 1 chale jaana, orientation ke time laila banke bhaukal macha dena, filmy acts perform karna, Mishra aur nunnu ki ladai karwa dena aur na jaane kitne kisse hai bhai teri bakchodiyo ke. Aisi koi cheez dimaag mein nahi aayi kabhi jo tu nahi kar sakta. Teri bakchodi exponentially badhi hai bhai first year se. Teri practical skills ka jawaab nahi bhai.

Jab bhi koi problem ya tension hui hai, tune hamesha sabse sahi advice di hai aur hamesha saath khada raha hai tu. Tere jitni bakchodi aur social skills mil paana bohot zyada mushkil hai bhai. Kaise manage kar leta hai sab? Goa mein bohot maza aaya tha yaar. Best trip thi vo meri aaj tak ki. Usse better trip agar hui to vo bhi tere saath hi hogi. Aakhri mahina to bhai jo protocols ki aisi ki taisi ki apan ne Hall 1 mein. Bohot sahi time tha yaar vo. Uske baad F3 mein to maje hi aa gaye the. Roz vahi khane ka jugaad bithana aur maal arrange karna, sab ekdum perfect tareeke se manage kiya hai tune. Kuchh bhi gossip hoti thi to sabse pehle tujhe pata chalta tha apne group mein. Hamesha se hi ekdum updated raha hai tu.

Movies dekh ke jo tu character ko portray karta hai, vo next level hai bhai. Itna involve ho jaata hai character mein ki kya hi kehna. Uss din Padmavat dekhne ke baad campus ka main gate todne wala tha tu, yaad hai na. Mere haath mein to bas camera hota tha, lekin videos agar aaj bakchod hai to vo teri wajah se. Kya sahi time tha na yaar campus wala. Abhi to bohot saari trips baaki hai yaar apni. Bete se baat ho gayi hai, Goa is on!!!

text:
Tujhse acha roommate nahi mil sakta yaar. Jab tu shuru mein aaya tha tab mujhe teri shakal mere ek Kota wale friend ke jaisi lagti thi XD. First year mein to kaafi faila ke rakhta tha tu samaan. Teri cupboard ka saara saamaan table aur chairs pe aa jaata tha sem end hote hote. Fir vahi, exam jab khatam hote the tab jamata tha wapas. Lekin abhi end tak aate aate kaafi zyada improvise kar liya hai tune, even mujhe beat kar diya safai ke maamle mein. Tera vo superman wala pose yaad hai jo tujhe Nupur ne karne ko kaha tha? Bohot hasi aayi thi tujhe uss getup mein dekh ke. Aur vo pizza challenge? Aadhe ghante soch ke question ka answer do aur unlimited Domino's khao. Mujhe vaise uska solution nahi pata tha, Mishra ka solution sunke kuchh bhi bol diya tha aur tu maan bhi gya lol. Uss din kitne pizza order huye the bhai. And uske baad bhi tujhe pata nahi kya chull hui ki tune aage aur bet laga li. Mishra ki wajah se bach gya tu verna to uss din bure lag gaye hote. Antaragni mein Coke Studio aur Local Train ke shows mein kya mast maje kiye the. Aur tera aur Mishra ka vo controller ke liye fight club karna. Ek baar to tumlog paper fight khel rahe the, jo towel fight mein convert ho gayi thi baad mein. Jab bhi kahi bahar se room pe aata tha to kuchh na kuchh bakchodi karta hua hi milta tha tu. Jhadu se jo tune Abhishek ko maara bhand hoke, aaha, saare sur aur taal mil gaye. Aur fir shoes pehen ke hi so gya bed pe. Cooridor ki aur teri haalat dekhte hi samajh gya tha ki kuchh hua hai. Aur uss din bete ka birthday yaad hai, jab apan thoda baith ke apne room wapas jaane wale the. Lekin tu dance karne lag gya tha aur mai room chala gya. Thodi der baad mai dekhta hu ki do log tujhe room pe laate hai, aur tujhse khada nahi hua jaa raha. Aise na jaane kitne karname kiye hai tune. Goa mein bhi kya sahi maze kiye the yaar. Uss din sofe pe jab tu bhand pada tha to kya bola tha club ka naam sunke yaad hai na? Yaad hai last day tumlog  bhand hoke shops mein gaaye jaa rahe the, aur sablog aate jaate tum logo ko hi dekh rahe the even shop ke log bhi. Best trip thi yaar vo.

Teri tarah itne different groups ka part har koi nahi reh sakta. Tu hamesha fit ho hi jaata hai kisi bhi group mein. Kaafi practical approach rehti hai teri decision lete time. Aur bakchodi ke liye to tu ever ready hai. Bas ek raaz raaz hi hai aaj tak ki tu hamesha dabba on rakhke kyu sota hai, bina dabba on rakhe neend nahi aati kya tujhe XP. Starting with VOX and DebSoc, NYO, PClub, Stamtatics, GSoC aur ab Stanford, tere chaapne ka level badhta hi jaa raha hai day by day. Aise hi grow karta reh. I am very happy ki Stanford jaa raha hai tu. Jaane se pehle ek trip to banti hai. Kya kehta hai boldu bete ko tickets book karne?

text:
Bhai abhi just check kiya, tera vo colour aa gya Samsung site pe. Bol order kardu?

Mujhe ekdum ache se to yaad nahi hai lekin jab apan first time mile the tab tu G-bot mein rehta tha. Pehli baar milne ke baad to hamesha milte hi rahe hai bhai. Hyderabad mein kitne maje kiye the bhai. Khandu ki harkatein. Ramoji jaate waqt Khandu kaise aage so gya tha. Aur poore raaste apan ne kaise record kiya tha XD. Ab to maan le ki tujhe uss time jhule pe jaane mein thoda dar laga tha XP. T-hub wali night photography bhai!! Uss din kaise apan paidal chale gaye the mall aur fir kapdo ke kaaran bina andar gaye hi wapas aa gaye the XD. Aur yaar ye panner puff aur Khandu ka kya majra hai? Dinner ki jagah paneer puff khake koi kaise itna fit reh sakta hai, yahi sochte rehte the apan lol. Aur uski jaw line wala discussion yaad hai? Vo canteen ka oreo shake to bhai!!! Jitna piyo utna kam. Karachi bakery aur death by Chocolate to yaad hi honge. Lekin undoubtedly sabse best vo idli aur tava bonda tha bhai DLF ke bahar. Uss din yaad hai apan peechhe wale section mein kaise police se chhup ke kha rahe the. Goa mein bhi kitne maje aaye the bhai. Poore time apan scooty pe hi ghoomte rehte the lol. April Fool wale din yaad hai kaisi fati thi F3 mein? Ye last mahina bohot sahi mil gya yaar apne ko.

Bohot sahi aadmi hai yaar tu. Campus ki agar koi khabar jaan ni ho to tu goto person hai without any second thoughts. Jab bhi kuchh help ya support chahiye hota hai to tujhse hi baat karta hu mai. Tere photography aur editing skills to bhai mashallah hai. Thanks for always being there!! Idli aur tava bonda at least ek aur baar to banta hai yaar.

text:
Pappu bhaye!!! First year mein depress rehne se leke F3 mein jaan fukne tak tumne bohot lamba rasta tay kiya hai.

First year mein to yaad hi nahi hai bhaye ki tumne kuchh bola bhi tha XD. Pehli official meeting mein tumne jab 5 minute mein Sachin ka sketch bana diya to seniors ki bhi ruh kaap gayi thi. Are unki chhodo, hume to laga tha ki gaya ye to ab. Lekin tumne sabke muh band kar diye. Shaanti se kaam karke saamne wale ki G maarna koi tumse seekhe. Fir to proper college posters banane lage the tum. Vo ladki kya sahi banayi thi pappu bhaye first year wale room mein. Harlem Shake bhi tumhara hi idea tha. Uske baad se to tumhara swag bas badhta hi gaya. Blue World mein kitne maje kiye the Pappu bhaye apan ne. Sab koi neeche wali slides pe hi jaa rahe the, apan to saari try kar chuke the almost. Ye nunnu nahi kudta to complete kar lete saari. Badhai Ho ke baad ki night photography yaad hai pappu bhaye? Pata nahi kya kya try kiya tha. Tumhara vo gardan wale tareeke se haan bolne ka andaaz alag hi hai. Aur uske saath saath agar muskan bhi mil jaaye tab to sone pe suhaga ho jaaye.

Uss din jab tum bhari garmi mein ganne ka juice leke aaye the sabke liye, tab to alag hi respect badh gayi thi tumhare liye XD. F3 kuchh nahi tha pehle, aaj agar itne logo ke muh pe F3 ka naam hai to bas tumhari wajah se. F3 mein kya kami hai aur usko kaise poora karna hai ye tumse behtar na kabhi koi samajh paaya hai aur na hi kabhi payega. F3 ke maje to kabhi nahi bhool sakte bhaye.

Silently kaam karke apna best effort dena tumhari sabse badi khoobi hai. Aur ye bhi ki tum seedhe muh pe sahi cheez bolte ho (jab bhi bolte ho XP). Apni trip nahi hui Pappu bhaye saath mein abhi tak. Gurgaon se Goa vaise utna zyada dur bhi nahi hai.

text:
Yo Champ!! Tujhe shayad nahi yaad lekin meko ache se yaad hai. Apan B-bot ke saamne wale cycle stand ke paas mile the pehli baar. Uske baad se to Mishra ke through milte hi rahe bhai. Mujhe lagta hai mere room se zyada time mai tumhare room pe raha hu. Raasta ekdum yaad sa ho gya tha bhai. Neend mein ya fir bhand hoke pohoch jaata tha mai tumhare room kitni baar to. D-bot wala room best tha bhai tum logo ka. Bohot masti ki hai apan logo ne vaha uss room mein.

Tujhse mila iss baat ki bohot khushi hai bhai. Ekdum genuine aur down to earth banda hai tu. Sahi tareeke se kaam karna tujhse seekhna chahiye bhai. Har kadam pe bohot help ki hai yaar tune. Chahe courses ho, tests ho ya aur koi bhi cheez ho. Ekdum proper aur sahi advice deta hai tu. Thoda sa bhi unsure hota hai to bata deta hai. Ye baat bohot sahi lagti hai yaar teri. text:
Ghar ka address mila ki nahi nunnu?

Tu literally pehla banda tha jisse mai campus mein mila tha. Upar se tu Vibrant se bhi tha. Vibrant sunke to dil khush ho gya tha. Campus aate hi tune jo apni bakchodi ka pitara khola, aaj tak hasi aati hai jab bhi teri baatein yaad aati hai. Meri baat maan aur stand-up comedy shuru kar de. Bohot aage jayega. Teri aur Mishra ki ladai ne hi mujhe camera se record karne ki aadat lagayi thi. Kaise ladte the be tum dono. Tu apni bakchodi side mein nahi rakhta tha aur Mishra apna ego side mein nahi rakhta tha. Kuchh bhi ho, lekin maza bohot aaya yaar. Aur Blue World to yaad hi hoga teko. Kya soch ke kuda tha tu 2 foot paani mein? Lagta nahi hai ki tujh mein itni jaan hogi lekin fight club mein to jhande gaad diye the tune. GPL mein bhi bohot tezz maarta hai tu, birthday boy ki to haalat kharab ho jaati hai tujhe dekh ke. Aur tera vo anguthe wala signature step yaad hai, jisne seniors ki bolti band kar di thi? Kaha se seekha tha be vo? Soumyadeep ki jo acting ki thi tune, bhai epic. Teri aur Pappu bhaye ki nok jhok bhi mast rehti thi yaar. Tere bina college life vaisi hi hai jaise bina tadke ki sabzi. Tera processor dikhwa le bhai, kaafi slow ho gya hai. Ab to lagta hai ki Ghajini ban ne hi wala hai tu. Trip nahi hui yaar apni saath mein. Bangalore aaja jaldi se, bete ki milke maarenge aur fir vahi se Goa chal denge. Are aur tera naach to dikha de ek baar. Meet ka link bhej du?
